<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Portfolio Website Development Proposal</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Calibri, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 36px;
      color: #111;
    }
    h1, h2, h3, h4 {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    p {
      margin: 6px 0;
    }
    ul {
      margin-top: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    li {
      margin: 3px 0;
    }
    .meta {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .package {
      border: 1px solid #d9d9d9;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .footer-space {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Portfolio Website Development Proposal</h1>

  <p class="meta"><b>Prepared By:</b> [Your Name]</p>
  <p class="meta"><b>Date:</b> [Insert Date]</p>
  <p class="meta"><b>Client Name:</b> [Insert Client Name]</p>

  <h2>1. Project Overview</h2>
  <p>
    This proposal outlines the scope, timeline, and pricing for building a professional portfolio website
    to showcase your work, achievements, and contact details.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Scope of Work</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Home Page (Introduction)</li>
    <li>About Section (Background)</li>
    <li>Projects / Work Showcase</li>
    <li>Skills / Services Section</li>
    <li>Contact Form (Google Sheet integration optional)</li>
    <li>Mobile-Friendly Responsive Layout</li>
    <li>Deployment (website live on internet)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Pricing Packages</h2>

  <div class="package">
    <p><b>BASIC - INR 15,000</b></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Up to 3 pages</li>
      <li>Simple professional design</li>
      <li>Mobile responsive</li>
      <li>Contact form</li>
      <li>Deployment</li>
    </ul>
    <p><b>Timeline:</b> 4-5 working days</p>
  </div>

  <div class="package">
    <p><b>STANDARD - INR 25,000</b></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Up to 5 pages</li>
      <li>Custom design</li>
      <li>Animations / interactions</li>
      <li>Basic SEO setup</li>
      <li>Deployment</li>
    </ul>
    <p><b>Timeline:</b> 7-10 working days</p>
  </div>

  <div class="package">
    <p><b>PREMIUM - INR 40,000</b></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Fully custom design</li>
      <li>Advanced UI and interactions</li>
      <li>Content update support / CMS</li>
      <li>SEO optimization</li>
      <li>1 month maintenance</li>
    </ul>
    <p><b>Timeline:</b> 12-15 working days</p>
  </div>

  <h2>4. Optional Services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Maintenance: INR 3,000/month</li>
    <li>Extra pages: INR 2,000/page</li>
    <li>Domain/Hosting setup: INR 2,000</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Payment Terms</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>50% advance before project start</li>
    <li>50% before final handover</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Revision Policy</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Up to 2 rounds of revisions included</li>
    <li>Additional revisions may be charged</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Client Responsibilities</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Provide content (text, images, branding details)</li>
    <li>Provide timely review and feedback</li>
    <li>Approve final output for launch</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>8. Acceptance</h2>
  <p>Client Name: ______________________________</p>
  <p>Signature: ________________________________</p>
  <p>Date: ____________________________________</p>

  <p class="footer-space">Thank you for considering this proposal.</p>
</body>
</html>
